Package filters

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    INodeFilter
    Takes either a single node or a list of nodes and picks which ones to keep based on the implementation's purpose.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NodeFilter_Downsample
    Filter which reduces the number of nodes in a list.
    NodeFilter_Identity
    Filter which accepts all nodes and rejects none.
    NodeFilter_MissingInfo
    Very new nodes might not have state or action assigned yet.
    NodeFilter_SurvivalHorizon
    Filters nodes based on survival past them to a specified horizon.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NodeFilter_Downsample.Strategy
    Available strategies for downsampling.
